contentfulBlogPost.title: TSConf JP が 2020年2月22日に開催！

childMarkdownRemark.html: TSConf JP is a TypeScript conference in Japan powered by TypeScript JP. This is the first event of TSConf in Japan. TypeScript involves together with ecosystem in recent years. Increase number of users, type inference got smarter and industry knowledge has accumulated. We would love to become a bridge between Japanese TSer and International TSer.
